name: Vampires
overview: A Paris teen who's half human, half vampire grapples with her emerging powers and family turmoil as she's pursued by a secret vampire community.

episodes.name: A High School Girl like Any Other
episodes.overview: Born into a family of vampires, high schooler Doina begins to rebel against her mother's strict rules — and the pills she's forced to swallow each day.

episodes.name: I'm a Monster
episodes.overview: Doina struggles to control her new urges. Deprived of blood, Rad and Irina turn against their  siblings. Andrea makes a deal with Ladislas Nemeth.

episodes.name: Your Old Life Is Gone Now
episodes.overview: As Doina is drawn deeper into the Nemeths' web, Martha races to help Andrea, and Elise sheds new light on Redouane's genetic research.

episodes.name: One Blood, One Rule, One Mother
episodes.overview: In exchange for a favor from Csilla, Doina agrees to attend a party and meet the community's matriarch. But the night takes an unexpected turn.

episodes.name: Everything Is Possible in This World
episodes.overview: Andrea and Elise undertake a daring mission to help the family. Nacer vows to find out where Doina lives. Csilla asks Ladislas to lay a trap.
